<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>coffeehack</title>
    <%- js('all') %>
    
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        font-size : 12px;
        font-family : "Courier", monospace;
      }
      #jshack {
        float : right;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size : 1.1em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="mainwrapper">
      <pre id="message"></pre>
      <canvas id="ch-canvas" width="640" height="480"></canvas>
      <!--<pre id="jshack"></pre>-->
      <pre id="status"></pre>
      
      <hr/>
      
      <div id="help">
        <h1>coffeehack</h1>
        roguelike game in your browser!
        <h1>key-bindings</h1>
        coffeehack's key-bindings are more or less similar to those of nethack.
        <table>
          <tr><td>h</td><td>move left</td></tr>
          <tr><td>j</td><td>move backward</td></tr>
          <tr><td>k</td><td>move upward</td></tr>
          <tr><td>l</td><td>move right</td></tr>
          <tr><td>&gt;</td><td>go down</td><td>Only valid when you are on a downward staircase cell</td></tr>
          <tr><td>&lt;</td><td>go up</td><td>Only valid when you are on a upward staircase cell</td></tr>
          <tr><td>y</td><td>answer yes to a question</td></tr>
          <tr><td>i</td><td>show inventory</td></tr>
          <tr><td>,</td><td>pick up an item on the floor</td></tr>
          <tr><td>w</td><td>wield a weapn</td></tr>
          <tr><td>d</td><td>drop an item</td></tr>
          <tr><td>x</td><td>auto-explore (buggy)</td></tr>
          
          <tr><td>anything else</td><td>rest on the current cell</td></tr>
        </table>
        <h1>ninjitsu</h1>
        There are special cells on the map which are shown as an "*" character (if you are playing the text-mode).
        When you are on that cell, you can use one of many ninjitsus that helps you defeating the monsters.
        A message should appear in the message area at the top asking you if you wanna use that jitsu or not.
        If you do, you press "y" key otherwise press any key other than "y".
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
